::Aerotaur::
       He smiles knowingly at Starstorm's last question.  "I'm afraid that 
the baby is still with the Maximals.  I ran into them on their way out and 
offered to watch the baby while they were 'working' as they Flicker here 
said.  That is why he did not return with the child."  He finally stretches 
and stands up.  "It would be advisable for you to take me to her now."

--part1_44.304e53c2.2bd4c718_boundary
